column2: "Emergency notice for all ARKS! Darker invasion in the urban sector of an ARKS ship has been confirmed!"
"An emergency protocol is in effect! I repeat, an emergency protocol is in effect!"
"All ARKS are to dispatch at once! Proceed to the ARKS ship urban sector at once!"
"Darker intrusion has been confirmed on ARKS Ship 128, the Themis."
"An emergency protocol is in effect! All ARKS are to dispatch from the quest counter immediately!"
"Because of your actions, a new story mission [Darker Storm] in now available at the mission counter."
